# Engineering rules

Rules are split by topic. Read the relevant file before editing matching `src/` areas.

- `functional-style.mdc` — Ramda, `pipe`/`compose`, `prAll`, guards, `tapAfter` patterns.
- `utils-and-modules.mdc` — `src/utils`, barrels, naming, logging namespaces.
- `hooks-policy.mdc` — CLI-first; React hooks policy when UI exists.
- `memory-and-concurrency.mdc` — `prAll` semantics, Playwright lifecycle, parallelism risks.
- `node-engines.mdc` — Node version floor and links to `package.json` / README.
